channel.title: Is it possible to get a different internet browser for itouch?
channel.description: Well the topic says it, but the reason i wnat this is because with firefox i would like to have the ability to have the addons, some of them are most helpful and i think on the itouch would save me putting things through my computer to put on to my itouch. cheers for any light you can shed
